    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国称以色列在战争“决定性时刻”提议停火</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-31/biden-raises-pressure-on-israel-hamas-for-deal-to-end-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国表示，以色列已提出新的加沙停火提议，将暂停与哈马斯的战斗至少六周，美国总统拜登称此举是加沙地带在几次和平尝试失败后冲突的“决定性时刻”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-31/biden-raises-pressure-on-israel-hamas-for-deal-to-end-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 May 2024 18:22:44 GMT</pubDate>
